### `BaseSlider` — `src/components/BaseSlider/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/Slider" — two variants: single-thumb (max only) and dual-thumb (range/min-max)
- **Props**: `modelValue?: number` (single, v-model), `minValue?: number` / `maxValue?: number` (range, v-model:minValue / v-model:maxValue), `min?: number` (default 0), `max: number` (**required**), `step?: number` (default 1), `range?: boolean` (default false), `trackMinLabel?: string`, `trackMaxLabel?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue`, `update:minValue`, `update:maxValue`
- **Track**: 4px height, `--color-neutral-80` unfilled, `--color-neutral-20` filled, 11px border-radius. Rendered as a custom div (not the native track) for full cross-browser control.
- **Thumb**: 24×24px solid `--color-neutral-20` circle; `cursor: grab` on hover, `cursor: grabbing` on active; focus ring `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px --color-accessibility-80`
- **Labels below track**: 14px/22px Roboto Regular `--color-neutral-40`; `8px gap` from track area to labels
- **Parent spacing**: parent should add `16px` gap between the companion label/input row and this component
- **Range fill**: single = `left:0, width: singlePercent%`; range = `left: minPercent%, width: (maxPercent - minPercent)%`
- **Dual-thumb overlap fix**: min input gets `z-index: 3` when `minPercent > 95%` so it remains reachable
- **Usage rules**: always pair with a label + value input above (never standalone); step and range determined per use-case by designer
- **Stories**: SingleDefault, SingleMidValue, SingleAtMax, SingleDisabled, RangeDefault, RangeMidValues, RangeDisabled, InteractiveSingle, InteractiveRange, InteractiveMonthlyPayment, InteractiveDownPayment, BothTypes

### `SegmentedControl` — `src/components/SegmentedControl/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/SegmentedControl" — pill-shaped track of 2–3 mutually exclusive options for view/filter switching
- **Props**: `options: SegmentedControlOption[]` (**required**, `{ value, label }`), `name: string` (**required**), `modelValue?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Auto-select**: emits `options[0].value` on `onMounted` if `modelValue` is empty (Figma: "first chip always auto-selected on page arrival")
- **Container**: `height: 38px`, `padding: 4px`, `border-radius: 42px`, `border: 1px solid --color-neutral-85`, `background: --color-neutral-100`, `gap: 1px` between chips
- **Chip**: `height: 30px`, `padding: 8px 16px`, `border-radius: 69px`, 14px/500 Roboto text
- **Chip states**: Default (no fill, Neutral0 text) → Hover (Neutral90 fill) → Selected (Primary50 fill, white text) → Focus (Selected + `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px --color-accessibility-80`)
- **Accessibility**: visually hidden `<input type="radio">`, `:has(:focus-visible)` for focus ring, `role="group"` on container
- **Usage rules**: max 3 options; always one selected; never use for dissimilar actions (use tabs or separate buttons instead)
- **Stories**: TwoOptions, TwoOptionsSecond, ThreeOptions, ThreeOptionsMiddle, Disabled, AllChipStates, Interactive, AutoSelect, SRPSortFilter

### `BaseRadio` — `src/components/BaseRadio/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/RadioButton" — single radio button; compose multiples into a group with a shared `name`
- **Props**: `value: string` (**required**), `name: string` (**required**), `modelValue?: string`, `label?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Anatomy**: 24×24px circle (outer ring) + 12×12px inner dot (shown when checked) + optional label text. Gap circle↔label: 12px.
- **List spacing**: 16px `gap` between radio items in a group.
- **Outer ring states**: Default 2px `--color-neutral-40` → Hover(unselected) 3px `--color-neutral-40` → Checked 2px `--color-base-primary-50` → Hover+Checked 2px `--color-base-primary-40` → Disabled 2px `--color-neutral-85`
- **Inner dot**: `--color-base-primary-50` (checked), `--color-neutral-85` (disabled+checked), hidden otherwise. Scale-in transition (0→1) on check.
- **Focus**: `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px --color-accessibility-80` on the circle (2px outside ring per Figma)
- **Hover text**: `text-decoration: underline` on label in hover state (both checked and unchecked)
- **Disabled**: `opacity: --opacity-level-medium`; never remove from DOM
- **Accessibility**: visually hidden `<input type="radio">` provides all semantics; parent should wrap group in `role="radiogroup"` with an `aria-label`
- **Label wrapping**: `align-items: flex-start` on the wrapper — long labels wrap and indent under the first character, not under the circle
- **Stories**: Default, Selected, Disabled, DisabledSelected, NoLabel, AllStates, RadioGroup, TwoColumn, LongLabel, WithDefaultSelection

### `ModalTabs` — `src/components/ModalTabs/`
- **Figma**: "Navigation/ModalTabs" — horizontal tabs for modals and slide-in panels only (not used standalone on pages)
- **Props**: `tabs: ModalTab[]` (**required**, `{ id, label }`), `modelValue?: string`, `showSeparator?: boolean` (default `true`)
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [id: string]`
- **Slot**: `#default="{ activeId }"` — parent shows/hides content with `v-show`
- **Auto-select**: emits first tab's id on `onMounted` if `modelValue` is empty
- **Keyboard**: roving tabindex; Left/Right arrows cycle between tabs
- **Accessibility**: `role="tablist"` on bar, `role="tab"` on buttons, `aria-selected`, `role="tabpanel"` on content
- **Tab anatomy**: `height: 34px` (16px label + 16px gap + 2px bar). `padding-right: 24px` creates spacing between tabs. Active indicator bar is `::after`, absolutely at `bottom: 0; right: 24px` so height transitions never shift layout.
- **Bar states**: no bar (default) → 1px (hover inactive) → 2px (active) → 3px (active+hover). All `--color-accent-40`.
- **Focus**: 2px `--color-accessibility-80` outline
- **Separator**: 1px `--color-neutral-80` line below tab bar — always shown in modal context
- **Overflow**: horizontal scroll on `.modal-tabs__bar`; right-edge white gradient fade via `.modal-tabs__fade` overlay
- **Usage rules** (Figma): max one tab active; first tab auto-selected; tabs only change content below (header stays static); tabs must be parallel in nature (use different pattern for dissimilar navigation)
- **Stories**: FeaturesAndSpecs, FirstTabAutoSelected, ManyTabsScrollable, TabBarOnly, NoSeparator, AllStates
- **Storybook `title`**: `Molecules/ModalTabs`

### `LogicSelector` — `src/components/LogicSelector/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/LogicSelectors" — compact inline single-choice picker that drives form logic (shows/hides fields)
- **Props**: `options: LogicSelectorOption[]` (**required**, `{ value, label }`), `name: string` (**required**), `modelValue?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`, `error?: string`
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Key UX rules**: No default selection on load (user must choose). State persists when user returns to the step. No "Continue" button needed.
- **Layout**: `inline-flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px`. Chip row uses `flex-wrap: wrap` so chips stack vertically on mobile. 8px gap between chips.
- **Chip size**: `height: 44px`, `padding: 8px 12px`, `border-radius: 4px`
- **Font**: Body SM (14px / 22px line-height, 400 weight)
- **Hidden radio inputs** for accessibility (`role="group"` on container)
- **States** (all via inset `box-shadow` — no layout shift):
  - Unselected: white bg, 1px `--color-neutral-85` border, `--color-neutral-40` text
  - Hover (unselected): `--color-neutral-90` bg, same border, same text + underline
  - Selected: `--color-neutral-20` bg (#313D47), same 1px border (subtle highlight), white text
  - Focus: 2px `#6fcfff` (Blue80) border on whichever chip has keyboard focus
  - Disabled: `opacity: --opacity-level-medium; pointer-events: none` on container
- **Error**: 12px `--color-warning-40` text below chip row, 4px gap (via `gap: 4px` on container)
- **Stories**: Default, WithSelection, HoverState, FocusState, ErrorState, Disabled, AllStates, DrivesFormFields, TradeIn, PaymentType, MobileWrapping

### `JourneySelector` — `src/components/JourneySelector/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/JourneySelectors" — one-click card that immediately routes the user into a flow
- **Props**: `label: string` (**required**), `selected?: boolean`, `disabled?: boolean`, `href?: string`, `target?: string`
- **Slots**: `#icon` — 24×24 SVG imported with `?raw` and wrapped in `<span v-html="..." style="display:contents" />`
- **Emits**: `select: [event: MouseEvent]`
