- **Layout-stable focus ring**: `border: 3px solid transparent` + `padding: 0 4px` reserved at all times so toggling `:focus-visible` never reflows the surrounding rows.
- **Brand awareness**: Uses the same global `--color-nav-*` tokens as `NavItem` / `NavItemMobile` and `--font-family-brand`.
