### `BaseButton` — `src/components/BaseButton/`
- **Figma**: "Buttons/Primary" (primary md), "Buttons/Tertiary" (primary sm), "Buttons/Secondary" (secondary light md), "Buttons/TertiaryOutlined" (secondary light sm), "Buttons/SecondaryDark" (secondary dark md), "Buttons/TertiaryDark" (secondary dark sm). Sonic equivalent: "Buttons" frame (`Primary` / `Secondary Dark` / `Secondary Light` × `Large` / `Small` × `Default` / `Hover` / `Pressed`).
- **Props**: `variant?: 'primary' | 'secondary'`, `size?: 'md' | 'sm'`, `theme?: 'light' | 'dark'`, `label?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]`
- **Sizes** (brand-driven via `--btn-md-*` / `--btn-sm-*` tokens):
 - `md` — EchoPark **56px h, 13px / 40px padding, 16px / 500 / 0.4px text**; Sonic **48px h, 12px / 24px padding, 18px / 700 / -0.198px / lh 1.3 text** (Sonic Figma "Large").
 - `sm` — EchoPark **40px h, 13px / 24px padding, 14px / 500 / 0 text**; Sonic **40px h, 12px / 16px padding, 14px / 700 / -0.154px / lh 1.3 text** (Sonic Figma "Small").
- **Border-radius**: EchoPark = pill (`--border-radius-pill`); Sonic = **2px** (`--button-border-radius` overridden in `primitives/sonic.css`).
- **Primary states**: hover (darker bg + underline), active (deepest bg, no underline), focus-visible (accessibility-blue ring via `border-color`), disabled (grey). Theme prop has no effect. Surface colours flow through `--color-btn-primary-surface[-hover|-press]` so brands can supply button-specific values that diverge from the broader `--color-action-primary` chain. **Sonic** overrides them to `#F24922 / #D9320D / #9A2409` (Figma button frame, slightly more orange than the rest of the Sonic primary palette).
- **Secondary states**: shape is identical across brands (2px → 3px inset box-shadow on hover, focus-visible = accessibility-blue ring, disabled = grey bg). Colours and press treatment are token-driven:
 - **EchoPark — light theme**: transparent surface, `--color-neutral-0` border + text, hover thickens to 3px (no fill change), press = 3px border + `--color-neutral-95` fill.
 - **EchoPark — dark theme**: white border + text on dark, hover thickens to 3px (no fill change), press = 3px border + `--color-neutral-0` fill.
 - **Sonic — light theme** ("Secondary Dark" in Figma): same outlined defaults as EchoPark, but **press keeps the border at 2px** and adds a `rgba(242, 242, 242, 0.10)` overlay fill (controlled via `--btn-secondary-press-border-width` and `--color-btn-secondary-surface-press`). Hover also adds an underline (Sonic-only structural override scoped via `[data-brand="sonic"]`).
 - **Sonic — dark theme** ("Secondary Light" in Figma): same white border / white text as EchoPark, but **press keeps the border at 2px** and uses `rgba(242, 242, 242, 0.10)` overlay (`--color-btn-secondary-surface-press-dark`). Same Sonic-only hover underline.
- **Brand override mechanics**:
 - Token swaps in `primitives/sonic.css` cover: border-radius, button typography (`--font-size-btn`, `--font-weight-btn`, `--line-height-btn`, `--letter-spacing-btn` and their `-sm` siblings), button dimensions (`--btn-md-height`, `--btn-md-padding`, `--btn-sm-*`), primary surface colours, secondary surface / border / text + press border-width.
 - `[data-brand="sonic"]` selector inside `BaseButton.vue` adds the secondary-hover underline that cannot be expressed as a token swap.
- **Stories**: full coverage of variant×size×theme×state + VariantComparison, SizeComparison, AllVariants. Plus **`Sonic — All States`** and **`Sonic — Secondary / Light (on dark bg)`** stories that mirror the Figma "Buttons" frame layout (3 variants × 2 sizes × 3 states) — switch the Storybook **Brand** toolbar to *Sonic Automotive* to see the Sonic styling. Dark-background stories use `backgrounds: { default: 'dark' }`.
- **Storybook backgrounds**: light (#FFFFFF), dark (#242C33), neutral-95 (#F4F5F7) — registered in `preview.ts`.
- **Key tokens used**: `--color-btn-primary-surface/-hover/-press`, `--color-btn-primary-text`, `--color-btn-secondary-surface/-hover/-press`, `--color-btn-secondary-surface-press-dark`, `--color-btn-secondary-border`, `--color-btn-secondary-text`, `--btn-secondary-press-border-width`, `--btn-md-height/-padding`, `--btn-sm-height/-padding`, `--button-border-radius`, `--font-*-btn*`, `--color-neutral-0/95/100`, `--color-focus-ring`.

